name: Regina Sampson
description: I am mature self-confident woman who knows exactly the man she needs. I like active rest, sport and my job! I might tell you that I am perfect but I think it will be not real. I like to tell truth and do not cheat or lie. As every person I have positive and negative qualities. I can be different. Sometimes I am romantic, dreamy and tender woman, who loves the color pink, a fluffy kitten and films about love. But sometimes I like to be sexy and fresh, with crazy, hot fantasies! I like to open borders! Yes, may be I am not perfect but I’m sure you will loose half of the world without me!
